---
// Branch management section with real screenshot
---

<section id="branches" class="py-20 md:py-32 relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute left-0 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-green/5 rounded-full blur-[150px] pointer-events-none"></div>

  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      <!-- Left: Screenshot -->
      <div class="order-2 lg:order-1 animate-on-scroll">
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-green/10 to-cyan/5 rounded-2xl blur-xl scale-105"></div>
          <div class="relative rounded-2xl border border-border overflow-hidden bg-bg-surface shadow-xl">
            <img 
              src="/images/branches-tab.png" 
              alt="FlowTree branches tab with searchable list, namespace grouping, and ahead/behind counts" 
              class="w-full h-auto"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: Text content -->
      <div class="order-1 lg:order-2 animate-on-scroll delay-2">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full border border-green/20 bg-green/5 text-green text-xs font-medium mb-6">
          <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M6 3v12" /><circle cx="18" cy="6" r="3" /><circle cx="6" cy="18" r="3" /><path d="M18 9a9 9 0 0 1-9 9" />
          </svg>
          Branch Management
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6 leading-tight">
          See what's checked out<br />
          <span class="text-green">and where.</span>
        </h2>

        <p class="text-text-secondary text-lg mb-8 leading-relaxed">
          Browse local and remote branches in a searchable view. Slash-based names are grouped into folders 
          so large branch lists stay manageable. Ahead/behind counts are shown directly in the list.
        </p>

        <ul class="space-y-4">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-green/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#4CAF7D" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12" /></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <span class="font-medium text-text-primary">Checked-out awareness</span>
              <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary mt-0.5">See where each branch is checked out — whether in the project root or a specific worktree. Warnings appear when a branch is already in use elsewhere.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-green/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#4CAF7D" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12" /></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <span class="font-medium text-text-primary">Safe branch operations</span>
              <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary mt-0.5">Checkout a branch into an existing worktree with a stash-first flow when it's dirty. Delete branches with explicit resolution choices when a worktree is using them.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-green/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#4CAF7D" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12" /></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <span class="font-medium text-text-primary">Pin and organize</span>
              <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary mt-0.5">Pin important branches to keep them at the top. Branch namespaces like <code class="text-xs bg-bg-elevated px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded font-mono">feature/*</code> are grouped into collapsible folders.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
